{"tid":1753732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【謝票】感激各位手足支持廁所板","createTime":"2019-11-25T04:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:54:49.000Z","uid":18648,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"04a70bbdb0c369fb0bb5aa13c0e5cbbfd32aa804","tid":1753732,"uid":18648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:16:38.000Z","msg":"小弟唔係一個特別醒嘅人<br />\n好彩有班義工<br />\n係背後不段提醒同鬧醒我<br />\n<br />\n有唔少街坊同我相認<br />\n一句「加油啊板仔」<br />\n我就已經感到好溫暖<br />\n<br />\n因為係住係康城入面<br />\n仲會有連登仔知我個朵<br />\n我就知道 大把手足撐我<br />\n<br />\n今日有2828票投比我<br />\n多謝每一位支持我同投票比我嘅手足<br />\n你地嘅每一票對於我段講<br />\n真心好多謝你地支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句<br />\n「光復香港<br />\n時代革命」<br />\n<br />\n我實在太攰<br />\n原諒我1999"},{"pid":"8b5d987b438d6d9c4a9878f1bc4ec6096751d83e","tid":1753732,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏左喇，但我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"13498188493e1be3c752c27688dc7313c11d76b5","tid":1753732,"uid":308588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60824a32c2267b9822d2bde053235b617c572434","tid":1753732,"uid":2615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"力撼康城土皇帝<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052066d7361fe07599ef631e5dc3b8ae4eee2716","tid":1753732,"uid":314443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:25:00.000Z","msg":"係我地心入面你已經贏晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再接再厲<br />\n好好增值自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係點票個陣真係好緊張<br />\n個心卜卜跳，第一次咁緊張一件事<br />\n好嬲展J𠝹你票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係唔好比我見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後你真係好叻仔<br />\n我以你為榮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />love u"},{"pid":"22d429c72d34e177752063003390ded8de512148","tid":1753732,"uid":314443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"好好休息，去放鬆一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b5612a776b61385354b12a6a21e8c32a0ca0b","tid":1753732,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4739546fc543f66d505a4c1f3a0f77164aa03b","tid":1753732,"uid":40317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ab7d75d6677072ce5000d2ea8f8b6301d9ceb1","tid":1753732,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T05:03:40.000Z","msg":"我愛你呀手足"},{"pid":"c51720d810321a33a4c958cff62e9b27b5697a2